来自外太空的不明飞行物
introduction: There is no telling what is really going on deep in space. But one thing is absolutely for certain, there is not one film or photo in this movie that was taken from earth. You will see real life UFOs captured in the far regions of space by NASA and foreign space agencies.在太空深处究竟发生了什么是不可知的。但有一点是绝对肯定的，这部电影中没有一部是从地球上拍摄的。你将看到美国宇航局和国外航天机构在遥远的太空区域捕捉到的真实的不明飞行物。
